data.description: Move In Ready, 3 bedroom 2 full bath home on large corner lot located in Foxchase Subdivision in Arab city limits. Updated kitchen with custom cabinets and granite countertops, separate dining room, vaulted ceiling in the living room with new wood flooring, natural gas fireplace and custom wood blinds. Lots of storage with walk in closets in all bedrooms, built-ins in the laundry room and living room. Full brick, large 2 car garage, beautiful landscaping and back deck. Come see this meticulously maintained home!
